# Privacy Policy (English)

**Effective date:** [2025-12-23]  
**App:** Vietnam Keyboard ([package: com.quocanh.vietnamkeyboard])  
**Developer:** Duong Quoc Anh  
**Contact email:** quocanh21081992@gmail.com

## 1. Overview
Vietnam Keyboard is an input method app that helps users type Vietnamese. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it.

## 2. Data we collect
We **do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data**, including but not limited to:
- Anything you type (keystrokes), messages, passwords
- Contacts, photos, location
- Device identifiers

## 3. How data is processed
As a **keyboard**, the app must process your input to provide typing functionality. This processing:
- Happens **locally on your device**
- Is **not** stored by the app
- Is **not** sent off the device

## 4. Permissions
The app may request permissions required to function as a system keyboard. We **do not** use these permissions to collect user data.

## 5. Third-party sharing
We **do not share** user data with any third parties.  
The app **does not** include ads/analytics SDKs (if this matches your current build).

## 6. Security
We follow a “privacy by design” approach: since we don’t collect data, there is no server-side user data to leak. If this changes in the future, we will update this policy.

## 7. Your rights (Data Subject Rights)
Because we **do not collect or store personal data**, we do not hold personal data to provide, correct, or delete from servers.

If you have any questions, contact:
- **Email:** [email@domain.com]

## 8. Children
The app is not directed to children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data from children.

## 9. Changes
We may update this policy when necessary. Updates will be posted on this page with a new effective date.
